add fragment to activity layout


<fragment android:name="edu.cseju.kessendra.fragment.ListFragment"
    xmlns:android="http://schemas.android.com/apk/res/android"
    android:layout_width="match_parent"
    android:layout_height="match_parent"
    android:id="@+id/list_fragment"
    />
    


on fragment class extend ListFragment


in onCreateView  change return type to super
initially it was 

return inflater.inflate(R.layout.fragment_list, container, false);

since we dont need layout for list fragment this inflate method conflict .   Thus change it to super.


    public View onCreateView(LayoutInflater inflater, ViewGroup container,
                             Bundle savedInstanceState) {

        ArrayAdapter<BeerDatabase> adapter = new ArrayAdapter<>(inflater.getContext(), android.R.layout.simple_list_item_1, BeerDatabase.bears);
        setListAdapter(adapter);

        return super.onCreateView(inflater,container,savedInstanceState);
    }
